# 🎣 Phishing Attacks: Recognize · Avoid · Stay Safe

> A comprehensive, visually-engaging security awareness presentation covering phishing email recognition, fake websites, social engineering tactics, real-world case studies, best practices, and an interactive quiz.

---

## 📋 Overview

This presentation was designed as a **Security Awareness Training module** to help individuals and organizations understand and defend against phishing attacks — one of the most prevalent and damaging cyber threats today.

Whether you're a security trainer, IT professional, educator, or team lead, this deck gives you everything you need to run an effective phishing awareness session.

---

## 🖥️ Slide Contents

| # | Slide Title | What's Covered |
|---|-------------|----------------|
| 1 | **Title Slide** | Topic overview and module tags |
| 2 | **What is Phishing?** | Definition, key statistics, attack type taxonomy |
| 3 | **Recognizing Phishing Emails** | Annotated fake email with 5 red flags |
| 4 | **Spotting Fake Websites** | Real vs. fake URL comparisons, verification checklist |
| 5 | **Social Engineering Tactics** | 6 psychological manipulation methods explained |
| 6 | **Best Practices** | 6 numbered action cards to stay protected |
| 7 | **Real-World Examples** | 3 high-profile phishing cases (Google/Facebook, Twitter, Twilio) |
| 8 | **Interactive Quiz** | 3 scenario-based questions with highlighted answers |
| 9 | **Action Plan** | Personal 5-step "Stay Phishing-Proof" plan |

---

## 🧠 Key Topics Covered

- **Email phishing** — recognizing spoofed senders, urgency tactics, suspicious links
- **Fake websites** — URL inspection, HTTPS verification, domain tricks
- **Social engineering** — urgency, fear, authority, greed, familiarity, reciprocity
- **Spear phishing, whaling, smishing & vishing** — attack type breakdown
- **Real-world breaches** — $100M Google/Facebook scam, Twitter Bitcoin hack, Twilio/Cloudflare attack
- **Best practices** — MFA, link verification, independent contact verification, password managers
- **Interactive quiz** — audience engagement with scenario-based questions

---

## 📊 Key Statistics Highlighted

- **3.4 Billion** phishing emails sent per day worldwide
- **36%** of all data breaches involve phishing
- **$17,700** lost per minute globally to phishing
- **74%** of organizations faced phishing attacks in 2023

